@startuml seq_17_save_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-17 Save Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Save Repo" as SaveRepo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open a post
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Click "Save"
Frontend -> Controller: (2.2) POST /api/posts/{id}/save
Controller -> Service: (3.1) Save post request
Service -> PostRepo: (3.2) Validate authentication and post state
PostRepo --> Service: (3.3) Post is valid

Service -> SaveRepo: (3.4) Check if already saved
SaveRepo --> Service: (3.5) Check result

alt Not yet saved
    Service -> SaveRepo: (5.1) Create saved-post record
    SaveRepo --> Service: (5.2) Record created
else Already saved
    Service -> Service: (4.1) Keep saved marker
end

Service --> Controller: (6.1) Updated saved state
Controller --> Frontend: (6.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (6.3) Update bookmark icon UI
@enduml
